@startuml
title Alarm Clock - State Diagram

[*] --> Off

state "Off" as Off
state "Alarm Set" as AlarmSet
state "Active" as Active
state "Ringing" as Ringing
state "Stopped" as Stopped

Off : do / System Initialization

AlarmSet --> Active : User Sets Time
Active : do / Check Current Time
Active --> AlarmSet : Not Matching
Active --> Ringing : Matches Set Time

Ringing : do / Start Ringing
Ringing --> Stopped : User Turns Off
Stopped : do / Save Next Alarm Time
Stopped --> Active : No Next Alarm

@enduml
